# APIsec CI/CD Demo — reference values
# These are added as GitHub Secrets + Variables in the repo settings,
# NOT as a local .env file. This example documents what you'll need.
#
# Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions

# Secrets (sensitive):
APISEC_USERNAME=your-apisec-login-email
APISEC_PASSWORD=your-apisec-login-password

# Variables (non-sensitive):
APISEC_PROJECT=run-scan-test
